  "notes": [
    "This file maps WoW addon folder names to their GitHub repositories",
    "Used for automated update checking and downloading",
    "installedVersion is synced from WTF/addons.json",
    "latestVersion is fetched from GitHub releases API",
    "Phase 2 features:",
    "  - Check-WowAddonUpdates: Compare installed vs latest versions",
    "  - Update-WowAddon: Download and install updates",
    "  - Watch-WowAddonUpdates: Real-time notification system",
    "GitHub MCP tools needed:",
    "  - github-mcp-server-actions_list (list releases)",
    "  - github-mcp-server-actions_get (get release details)",
    "  - Download release assets via direct URLs",
    "Asset patterns:",
    "  - Most addons release as .zip files",
    "  - Some have -nolib variants (exclude if using packaged libs)",
    "  - Extract to WoW/_retail_/Interface/AddOns/<installPath>"
